# Example agent script — run with: ./zagctl run examples/agent_demo.tcmd
request demo-new current new
request demo-plate current place plate 0 0 0 0
request demo-emitter current place emitter 1 1 2 0
request demo-chamber current place chamber 4 1 3 0
request demo-detector current place detector 7 1 4 0
request demo-route-a current route 2 0 3 0
request demo-route-b current route 3 3 4 0
sim step 16
sim state
request demo-save current save /tmp/agent_demo.zpa
render /tmp/agent_demo.bmp
list
